    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">The Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  Shadow Stalker is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror experience. One player takes on the role of <strong>“The Hunted,”</strong> a near-invisible monstrosity armed with supernatural abilities, while 2–8 other players team up as <strong>“The Hunters,”</strong> a well-equipped elite task force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">...Over here...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  The Hunted thrives in the shadows, barely perceptible to the naked eye. Despite the number of Hunters outnumbering The Hunted, The Hunted’s unique powers can even the odds:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spectral distortion </strong>– They can't shoot what they don't see.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/bc72f26874b30bf5e4b10e2235762ee6.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1170 height=730 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/bc72f26874b30bf5e4b10e2235762ee6.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/bc72f26874b30bf5e4b10e2235762ee6.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wall Climbing</strong> – Scale walls, crawl along ceilings, and strike from impossible angles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/66352bfc14f0a3008b15a270d6827680.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1170 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/66352bfc14f0a3008b15a270d6827680.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/66352bfc14f0a3008b15a270d6827680.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raise the Dead</strong> – Reanimate defeated NPCs and players to create a shambling horde that can sniff out  the hunters. <br>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/3b8e41a98235c543255d25242079c909.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1170 height=746 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/3b8e41a98235c543255d25242079c909.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/3b8e41a98235c543255d25242079c909.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">Hunt or Be Hunted</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Step into the boots of a Hunter, a member of an elite squad tasked with bringing down The Hunted. Work as a team, keep your eyes peeled, and use advanced tactics to corner your prey. Armed with high-tech weapons and gadgets, you’ll need to stay alert; or you might just find yourself on the receiving end of the hunt.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Custom loadouts </strong>– Customize your loadouts for maximum survivability.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/fda6ddd84977d7fcd54401147e4b1d10.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/fda6ddd84977d7fcd54401147e4b1d10.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/fda6ddd84977d7fcd54401147e4b1d10.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gadgets </strong>– Placeable to give hunters the illusion of safety.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/d370985c6358b612f35d89bc5c650371.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1050 height=692 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/d370985c6358b612f35d89bc5c650371.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/d370985c6358b612f35d89bc5c650371.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And overall hijinks...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/72c7d146fe44ee7c0735c6a25c58ba2a.poster.avif?t=1770446989\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/72c7d146fe44ee7c0735c6a25c58ba2a.webm?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364290/extras/72c7d146fe44ee7c0735c6a25c58ba2a.mp4?t=1770446989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
